ing: 2 (5 ounce) containers sharp processed cheese food
2 bunches green onions, finely chopped, white parts only
des: "This is a great cheese dip!  It's easy to make and has only a few ingredients. Plenty of green onions blend well with the soft cheeses. Slice up bagels for dipping. It's a big hit every time I take it to a party. "
ins: In a medium bowl, mix together the cream cheese, sharp processed cheese food and green onions until well blended.
